title: Nature sounds, Sleep sounds, relaxation,  to make you sleepy
description:
THIS TORRENT IS NATURE SOUNDS ONLY, NO MUSIC (THE WAY I LIKE IT)
P.S. IF ANYONE CAN FIND THE NAMES OF SOME OF THE UNLABELED ONES, PLEASE FEEL FREE TO POST IN COMMENTS. I TRIED EVERY PROGRAM I KNEW OF TO RECOGNIZE THE FILES, AND THEY COULDNT.
FEEL FREE TO SHARE THESE FILES IF YOU LIKE.

this torrent has a variety of different sleep sounds, sleep music that I have narrowed down to be the best, in my opinion of all the sleep cd's i've listened to.
I have about 35 dvds worth of sleep files. I loaded them onto my computer player, and listened to them all, then narrowed them down simply by deleting the ones that i didn't think were superior.
i think you will find a great variety and if you burn all these to a dvd, i think you will have plenty to change up from for a long time.
my most favorite is the rain one called Ruth Ann Goode, PhD - Heavy Rain and Thunder  if i had to choose one to listen to for life it is this one
